SECOND REGULAR SESSION
SENATE BILL NO. 1131
103RD GENERA L ASSEMBLY
INTRODUCED BY SENATOR BROWN (26).
5371S.01I KRISTINA MARTIN, Secretary
AN ACT
To repeal sections 137.115, 137.750, 138.380, 138.390, 138.410, and 138.435, RSMo, and to enact
in lieu thereof six new sections relating to the duties of the state tax commission.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Missouri, as follows:
1 Section A. Sections 137.115, 137.750, 138.380, 138.390,
2 138.410, and 138.435, RSMo, are repealed and six new sections
3 enacted in lieu thereof, to be known as sections 137.115,
4 137.750, 138.380, 138.390, 138.410, and 138.435, to read as
5 follows:
1 137.115. 1. All other laws to the contrary
2 notwithstanding, the assessor or the assessor's deputies in
3 all counties of this state including the City of St. Louis
4 shall annually make a list of all real and tangible personal
